><dc:creator><![CDATA[CitizenK9]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Given that the evidence already proves everything that needs to be proved, the trial should last one day and then the execution. Save money and time.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qN0Rt1O</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ue8iBzy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qN0Rt1O</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lassannn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>He pulled out that sword so fast</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0VHYmtw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EWfSPRG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0VHYmtw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[VentiTheButler]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>He’s the best</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NTpi4r3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TwghAMj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NTpi4r3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rossthomas12]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ma'am.  You dropped your ball.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/phFcoUq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bww7dHb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/phFcoUq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeirdAlisMySpiritUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Oops</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sJtiBbg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JRjOAjH.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tweet link : https://twitter.com/brianklaas/status/1525933883593740290</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sJtiBbg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mech0T1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Miracle is not strong enough</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KmVONRP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/501nnGF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Update 2: Thank you is not even a satisfactory phrase to the overwhelming support the Imgur community has shown myself and my family. We have received enough to assist our immediate need.  I have removed the link and I hope you spread your generous nature to others in a similar situation.  Thank you again Imgurians.  

Update: I want to send a huge thank you to everyone who has been kind enough to send coffees on the Kofi link. This community here on Imgur is always shown that they are amazing and has restored so much faith in humanity to me.  If it is not working anymore I have not disabled did PayPal has decided to restrict my account and I am currently fighting with them to unrestrict my account.  

I'm a teacher..and a mom of 4...husband's work cut him to one day a week and then just flat-out didn't pay him.  We're only behind 10 days on rent and I had to choose between paying for food, gas, electric, and water over the rent because I didn't have enough to pay both. Last night the landlord delivered a 3 days to pay or vacate the premises notice. It's  3 weeks left in the school year I'm coordinator of the graduation. I have to hide all of this for my work and my kids and my students. Shelters won't take us and we can't afford to go anywhere else. Family only suggests going to a shelter or applying for Aid a few of my family members are more than well off enough to spare $1,700. They're so we had to touch because according to agencies that provide financial aid and food stamps we make too much money. What they don't realize is a shelter only take me unless my husband leaves me if you don't want able-bodied men in the shelters. Most of the places just won't even answer the phone. The past six months have driven to work on gas fumes and prayers.  I go to work with a smile even though chaos in my world is falling apart behind the scenes.  Thank you for letting me vent. We have sold most of our furniture and anything of value just so you can pay the bills I mentioned above. The only thing I have left of any value is my car and I need to get to work. Sometimes I feel and beg for death because my life insurance policy is worth more.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KmVONRP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sacrificialteacher2020]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cows</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/H8pMtcf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b2yr1ll.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/H8pMtcf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[alexjones09992718]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>